Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were furious earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forgetting your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that I'm just a talented matador\Nwho can make things ripple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you'd be the strongest\Nin the Colosseum's history forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a solid strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current hero of the Colosseum is\Nme, Diamante-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current hero of the Colosseum is\Nme, Diamante-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can make things ripple as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Army Bandera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try! You almost got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been running around \Nthe country all day today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fighting while protecting your daughter's life\Non this wavering ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just one leg! If you \Nwere an ordinary person,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've been unable to move already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}, how's Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0} doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Kyros is almost \Nreaching his limit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please avenge Scarlet-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to concern yourself about\Nmy having one leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wanted to use it as an excuse,\NI wouldn't have come to this battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dedicated my missing leg to someone \NI owed a lot to and I'm proud of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then, I don't have to hesitate\Nto strike your weak point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too boring for me to just deliver a \Nfinal blow to the already-fatigued you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Those are...\N--...Confetti?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They look \Nlike just paper but they're
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,actually something that I made to ripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll undo my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ripple Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiked iron balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how beautiful they are!\NIt's like stardust!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N--I guess we have nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robiland! Please protect Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're upset. You know what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, those are stardust that \Ncan kill an entire army!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's extremely difficult to stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we're at the Sunflower Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blooming beautifully, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adios!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Enjambre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower Umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she handles it quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An army that gets defeated by an attack \Nlike this mustn't be that good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's smacking away every \Nsingle spiked iron ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he can even \Navoid getting wet in rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out for what's falling onto you, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How silly are you to stumble now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Diamante! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Rebecca! There are still iron balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the gun that I shot\Nyour wife Scarlet with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy!\NYou'll get killed with my gun like your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you! Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Rebecca! Don't forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me! I'll kill you with these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}! I gotta kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long will it last?!\NThe Flower Umbrella can't take it anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} fight! Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a decade, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NGet under the umbrella! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have followed your mother's wish!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said I shouldn't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you how to not get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has never hurt anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she won it all by letting \Nopponents fall out of the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has never been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even cut your enemy\Nand you call yourself a winner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shed your blood, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a horrible match!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought shame to all of us gladiators!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Drop dead, Rebecca!\N--A corrupted family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You foul-blooded wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been fighting in the Colosseum\Nbut you still haven't hurt anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are still clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in which your mother \NScarlet's spirit lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother-sama...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to bathe \Nthose hands with the blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of a devil like him after all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you wield a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:27.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His entire body assailed by \Ncountless deadly iron balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:28.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros reaches his limit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when he thinks of the pain and grief
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that Doflamingo caused to the citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gets filled with resentment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:38.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}his wholehearted attack which will
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:40.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,tear up the misfortune \Nof Dressrosa is launched!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Trueno Bastardo! Kyros' Furious Strike!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
